Class Move

java.lang.Object
  Move

public class Move
extends Object

Represents a single move, in which a piece moves to a destination location. Since a move can be undone, also keeps track of the source location and any captured victim.

Version:
May 27, 2015
Author:
Alyce Brady, APCS Development Committee, Cay Horstmann, Anu Datar
